<HEADLINE>
<P>
TODAY'S QUOTE 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
"I see less garbage in the East River than Santa Monica Bay. The East River is 
getting cleaner while the Santa Monica Bay is getting dirtier." 
</P>
<P>
 -- Pat Hines, world class endurance swimmer, saying she became ill after 
training in the Santa Monica Bay on Saturday. 
</P>
</TEXT>
<TYPE>
<P>
Column 
</P>
</TYPE>
