Gannett Co.: The Washington-based diversified news and information company 
reported second-quarter profit of $112 million, up 15% over a year ago. Revenue 
totaled $904 million, up 7%. The results reflected a 6% gain in newspaper 
advertising revenue, while circulation revenue rose 4%. Broadcasting revenue 
