GOVERNMENT OFFICIALS; LOS ANGELES -- GOVERNMENT AGENCIES; LOS ANGELES -- 
FINANCES; GANGS -- LOS ANGELES; CRIME -- LOS ANGELES; COMMUNITY SERVICE 
PROGRAMS; CRIME PREVENTION 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
