-- PUBLIC LANDS; NEVADA -- PUBLIC LANDS; HANSEN DAM; SANTA MONICA MOUNTAINS; 
ELSMERE CANYON; MISSION CANYON; RUSTIC CANYON; SULLIVAN CANYON; FRANKLIN 
CANYON; LOPEZ CANYON LANDFILL; DUMPS -- LOS ANGELES COUNTY; LEGISLATION -- 
