SAVINGS &amp; LOAN ASSOCIATION; AMERICAN CONTINENTAL CORP; BANKRUPTCY; 
POLITICAL CONTRIBUTIONS; KEATING, CHARLES H JR; CALIFORNIA -- SUITS; JUNK BONDS 
