sweeping novel. Burning of Atlanta was recreated on Culver City lot, with 
nervous Fire Department officials standing nearby. ; Photo, Copyright 1981 by 
Darlene G. Parrish and William J. Tomkin ; Photo, Historical society officials 
Joy Jacobs and Julie Lugo Cerra and society President Marti Diviak stand by 
window prop used in "Gone With the Wind." CASSY COHEN / Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</GRAPHIC>
